column2:
"Let's go full throttle!
Be sure to keep up!"

"Shine your lights and let's join the dazzling sea of stars!
『Cosmic twinkle star』!"

"Gliding from past to future
like a shining jet coaster"

"Look to the future,
and step forth to our dreams"
"Let's set sail amongst the sea of twinkling stars"
"And have the adventure of our lives"

"Let the future song echo
far beyond the horizon"
"The unknown flashing skies will be our stage"

"For tomorrow will always be
our guiding light"

"Galaxy of twinkling stars,
light up our dreams"
"So that our dearest wishes are always in sight"
"Let's set sail amongst the sea of twinkling stars"
"And have the adventure of our lives"

"Let the future song echo
far beyond the horizon"

"Galaxy of twinkling stars,
light up our dreams"
"So that our dearest wishes are always in sight"
"Will become the miracle of light in our universe"
